title: Top 10 Running Back Rankings: Zeke or Saquon? Does Todd Gurley still belong? (Football 7/1)
description:
Offensive Rankings Week continues with a look at the best running backs in the NFL. Patrik Walker joins host Will Brinson to explain and defend his Top 10. Alvin Kamara is not one of those Top 10...How can that be? Where do former top picks like Leonard Fournette and Todd Gurley land? Remember, it's important to look at past production but also weigh in expected 2020 performances. Who's the best back from the state of Ohio: Nick Chubb or Joe Mixon? Who's the best back in the NFC East: Saquon Barkley or Ezekiel Elliott? All those answers plus a not-so-surprising pick at #1.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
